<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lab 6 - Lista de Cumparaturi</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #eef3f9;
            --panel: #ffffff;
            --primary: #24508a;
            --primary-strong: #18385f;
            --accent: #f3b53f;
            --text: #1f2d3d;
            --muted: #607086;
            --border: #d9e2ee;
        }        /* Stiluri pentru populare și seed */
        .user-info {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-top: 4px;
            display: block;
        }

        .seed-badge {
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        /* Stiluri pentru validare și mesaje de eroare */
        .error-msg {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #b91c1c;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .btn-delete {
            background: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .search-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        /* Stiluri pentru teme dinamice */
        body.dark {
            --bg: #1a1a1a;
            --panel: #2d2d2d;
            --text: #e0e0e0;
            --muted: #a0a0a0;
            --border: #444;
        }


        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(243, 181, 63, 0.28), transparent 22%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #f7faff 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-strong) 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 32px 20px 48px;
        }

        .wrap {
            width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.1rem);
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        .hero-card,
        .card {
            background: var(--panel);
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(27, 46, 78, 0.12);
        }

        .hero-card {
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 22px;
        }

        .actions,
        .menu {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .button,
        .menu a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 11px 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .button.primary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #172030;
        }

        .button.secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        }

        main {
            padding: 26px 0 40px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .card {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h2,
        h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .muted {
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        ul,
        ol {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 12px 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background: #f6f8fc;
        }

        .pill {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: #e7eef8;
            color: var(--primary-strong);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--muted);
            padding: 0 0 26px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 820px) {
            .hero {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="wrap hero">
            <section>
                <div class="menu">
                    <a href="#cerinte">Cerintele Implementate</a>
                    <a href="#exemple">Exemple Produse</a>
                    <a href="#pasi">Cum Rulezi</a>
                </div>
                <h1>Aplicatie Lista de Cumparaturi</h1>
                <p>
                    Pagina aceasta prezinta tema de Lab 6 construita pornind de la codul initial din
                    <strong>3.html</strong> si extinsa intr-o aplicatie completa cu Express, EJS, sesiuni,
                    cookie-uri si rute protejate.
                </p>
                <div class="actions">
                    <a class="button primary" href="http://localhost:3000" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Deschide Aplicatia</a>
                    <a class="button secondary" href="#pasi">Vezi Pasii de Pornire</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <aside class="hero-card">
                <h3>Rezumat rapid</h3>
                <p class="muted">Tema include autentificare, dashboard, lista personala, setari tema si persistenta in memorie pe utilizator.</p>
                <span class="pill">Express</span>
                <span class="pill">EJS</span>
                <span class="pill">Sessions</span>
                <span class="pill">Cookies</span>
                <span class="pill">Middleware</span>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="wrap">
        <section class="grid" id="cerinte">
            <article class="card">
                <h2>Ce am implementat</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Inregistrare si autentificare utilizator.</li>
                    <li>Rute protejate pentru dashboard si lista mea.</li>
                    <li>Sesiuni pentru utilizatorul logat si numar de vizualizari.</li>
                    <li>Cookie-uri pentru ultima vizita, tema si ultima categorie.</li>
                    <li>Middleware propriu pentru logarea activitatii.</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
                <h2>Structura proiectului</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>app.js</strong> pentru configurarea serverului.</li>
                    <li><strong>views/</strong> pentru paginile EJS.</li>
                    <li><strong>middleware/</strong> pentru logare si protectie rute.</li>
                    <li><strong>db/</strong> pentru datele simulate.</li>
                    <li><strong>public/</strong> pentru stiluri.</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
                <h2>Date initiale</h2>
                <p class="muted">Am pastrat tema listei de cumparaturi din codul tau initial si am folosit produse exemplu pentru utilizatorul demo.</p>
                <p><strong>Cont demo:</strong> admin / admin123</p>
            </article>
        </section>

        <section class="card" id="exemple">
            <h2>Exemple de produse din aplicatie</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Produs</th>
                        <th>Categorie</th>
                        <th>Cantitate</th>
                        <th>Pret</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Mere</td>
                        <td>Fructe</td>
                        <td>2</td>
                        <td>4.50 RON</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Paine</td>
                        <td>Panificatie</td>
                        <td>1</td>
                        <td>3.00 RON</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Apa minerala</td>
                        <td>Bauturi</td>
                        <td>6</td>
                        <td>2.20 RON</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <section class="grid" id="pasi">
            <article class="card">
                <h2>Pasii de rulare</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Deschizi terminalul in folderul proiectului.</li>
                    <li>Rulezi <strong>npm install</strong>.</li>
                    <li>Optional copiezi <strong>.env.example</strong> in <strong>.env</strong>.</li>
                    <li>Rulezi <strong>npm start</strong>.</li>
                    <li>Accesezi <strong>http://localhost:3000</strong>.</li>
                </ol>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
                <h2>Legatura cu 3.html</h2>
                <p class="muted">
                    Codul initial a fost o pagina HTML cu tema lista de cumparaturi si exemple de produse.
                    In versiunea actuala, aceeasi idee a fost extinsa intr-o aplicatie web completa pentru cerintele din Lab 6.
                </p>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        Proiect pregatit pentru tema Lab 6, pe baza codului tau initial.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
